thread.title: Christopher Jacobellis

author: Christopher Jacobellis
title: Christopher Jacobellis
text: Needed my 2010 Chevy Cobalt air bag module reset. It would have cost me over $500.00 at the dealer plus labor. My Air Bags cost me only $40.00 plus shipping and I had my module reset and back to me within a week. Air bag light went out as needed. These guys are great and are very knowledgeable. I would recommend them to anyone and use them again in the future. Thank you again
